snippet.title: Diffusion - gameplay trailer
snippet.description:
Diffusion is a total-conversion mod for Half-Life, running on Xash3D engine. It will feature around 8 hours of single-player content and also has full multiplayer support. Some parts of the video are still work in progress and can feature placeholders.
Follow the mod on ModDb: https://www.moddb.com/mods/diffusion
Music is also written by me as a part of Traceline project: https://traceline.bandcamp.com
